{"parse":{"title":"Message Markers","pageid":2915,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"df60bf18efe7500adba15a8676604475\">VTS</span>-2012-20</b>\n</p><p>In order to especially facilitate shore-to-ship and ship-to-shore communication or when one of the <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"b6f60f2f331c5ad04e19a91d0ba388f4\">IMO</span> Standard Marine Communication Phrases will not fit the meaning desired, one of the following eight message markers may be used to increase the probability of the purpose of the message being properly understood.\n</p>\n<ul><li>Instruction</li>\n<li>Advice</li>\n<li>Warning</li>\n<li>Information</li>\n<li>Question</li>\n<li>Answer</li>\n<li>Request</li>\n<li>Intention</li></ul>\n<p><br>\nSource: <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"b6f60f2f331c5ad04e19a91d0ba388f4\">IMO</span> <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"7fc56270e7a70fa81a5935b72eacbe29\">A</span>.918(22)\n</p><p>(VTS33/output/8 refers) \n</p>\n<div class=\"LanguageLinks\">\n<table width=\"100%\">\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\" style=\"background: #FFFFFF\">\n<td style=\"width: 25px; padding-left: 0em; border-right: 1px solid #aaaaaa;border-left: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-top: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-bottom: 1px solid #EEF3E2;\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:25px-Geographylogo.png\" class=\"mw-file-description\" title=\"Languages\"><img alt=\"Languages\" src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/8/82/25px-Geographylogo.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></td>\n<td style=\"padding: 1px 1em 0; background: #EEF3E2;\">\n<p><b><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">English</a></b>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"df60bf18efe7500adba15a8676604475\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Vessel Traffic Services\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"b6f60f2f331c5ad04e19a91d0ba388f4\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>International Maritime Organization\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"7fc56270e7a70fa81a5935b72eacbe29\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>ampere\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260615100531\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.036 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.043 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 58/1000000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 658/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 203/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/100\nExpensive parser function count: 4/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   12.882      1 Template:Languages\n100.00%   12.882      1 -total\n 61.76%    7.957      4 Template:Languages/Lang\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wiki_iala_dictionary_1_41:pcache:idhash:2915-0!canonical and timestamp 20260615100531 and revision id 9825. Rendering was triggered because: page-view\n -->\n</div>"},"langlinks":[],"categories":[{"sortkey":"","*":"9.1_VTS_terms"},{"sortkey":"","*":"Alphabetical_Index"},{"sortkey":"","*":"IALA_Dictionary_2012_Revision"},{"sortkey":"","*":"IALA_Dictionary_2023_Revision"}]}}